leave when he woke up.

790
00:40:17,723 --> 00:40:19,353
But it all happened so suddenly.

791
00:40:19,853 --> 00:40:21,693
I'm not sure what to say.

792
00:40:21,753 --> 00:40:23,653
Just don't say anything.

793
00:40:23,983 --> 00:40:25,883
You're driving me crazy.

794
00:40:28,083 --> 00:40:29,853
Since it came to this,

795
00:40:30,253 --> 00:40:31,583
Ms Oh should...

796
00:40:31,753 --> 00:40:33,983
take care of President so that he can rest.

797
00:40:34,193 --> 00:40:36,653
What are you talking about?
She's not staying.

798
00:40:36,823 --> 00:40:39,083
We don't have any other choice.

799
00:40:41,753 --> 00:40:43,353
I'm home.

800
00:40:43,623 --> 00:40:45,882
Hi, Hyun Ji. You're late.

801
00:40:45,883 --> 00:40:48,193
- How's Grandpa? - He got discharged.

802
00:40:48,753 --> 00:40:49,753
Dad.

803
00:40:50,083 --> 00:40:51,383
Can we talk?

804
00:40:53,653 --> 00:40:55,553
My princess!

805
00:40:55,623 --> 00:40:57,723
What do you want to talk about?

806
00:40:58,253 --> 00:40:59,283
- Dad. - Yes.

807
00:40:59,353 --> 00:41:00,883
I have something I want to ask you.

808
00:41:00,983 --> 00:41:02,653
Can you be honest with me?

809
00:41:02,723 --> 00:41:05,653
Well, what is it?

810
00:41:06,753 --> 00:41:08,623
Were you the one who kicked out...

811
00:41:08,693 --> 00:41:09,753
Sung Min's dad?

812
00:41:12,383 --> 00:41:13,623
What are you talking about?

813
00:41:14,253 --> 00:41:15,753
Why would I do that?

814
00:41:16,783 --> 00:41:18,083
Let me rephrase that.

815
00:41:18,953 --> 00:41:20,883
Did you do something to Sung Min?

816
00:41:24,193 --> 00:41:25,883
Did he say something?

817
00:41:26,353 --> 00:41:28,483
Did he say that I did
something wrong to him?

818
00:41:28,583 --> 00:41:31,083
No, I'm asking you because
he won't tell me.

819
00:41:32,253 --> 00:41:34,583
There's something for sure,
but he won't tell me.

820
00:41:36,283 --> 00:41:37,353
He's avoiding me.

821
00:41:39,753 --> 00:41:41,983
Hyun Ji, I didn't do anything.

822
00:41:42,353 --> 00:41:43,983
Really? Can I trust you?

823
00:41:44,083 --> 00:41:45,193
Of course.

824
00:41:46,483 --> 00:41:47,553
Dad.

825
00:41:47,853 --> 00:41:50,693
I hope you never disappoint me.

826
00:41:52,193 --> 00:41:53,623
You know what I mean, right?

827
00:41:55,883 --> 00:41:57,283
Of course.

828
00:42:13,583 --> 00:42:16,483
(Stop the redevelopment project,
Choongshim Construction)

829
00:42:32,723 --> 00:42:33,723
What are you doing?

830
00:42:36,083 --> 00:42:37,253
Oh.

831
00:42:40,283 --> 00:42:41,883
- What is this? - It's...

832
00:42:42,483 --> 00:42:44,083
It's galbi.

833
00:42:44,253 --> 00:42:45,983
Cook some for your dad.

834
00:42:46,453 --> 00:42:47,623
You should have some, too.

835
00:42:47,693 --> 00:42:48,853
Are you kidding me?

836
00:42:49,283 --> 00:42:50,583
What are you trying to pull?

837
00:42:51,083 --> 00:42:53,283
Do you think you can bribe
us with something like this?

838
00:42:54,353 --> 00:42:55,753
You're from that German bar, right?

839
00:42:55,883 --> 00:42:57,383
I guess you finally remembered.

840
00:43:00,553 --> 00:43:01,853
There are no words...

841
00:43:02,383 --> 00:43:04,083
that could express how sorry I am.

842
00:43:04,253 --> 00:43:05,813
Are you going to be me for forgiveness?

843
00:43:10,083 --> 00:43:11,753
What happened...

844
00:43:12,253 --> 00:43:13,723
to your dad?

845
00:43:13,753 --> 00:43:16,283
After what happened to our store,
he fell ill from the shock.

846
00:43:16,853 --> 00:43:18,453
You gangsters...

847
00:43:18,483 --> 00:43:20,353
broke my family apart.

848
00:43:29,693 --> 00:43:30,693
By the way,

849
00:43:31,453 --> 00:43:32,653
what did Choongshim Construction say?

850
00:43:32,883 --> 00:43:34,083
Do they want you to leave?

851
00:43:34,983 --> 00:43:36,223
I'm sure that's what they said.

852
00:43:36,883 --> 00:43:38,723
That's how it was like when I was there.

853
00:43:39,383 --> 00:43:40,483
So what?

854
00:43:41,653 --> 00:43:42,723
Are you telling me...

855
00:43:42,753 --> 00:43:44,713
to give up if I don't want
to end up like my dad?

856
00:43:48,353 --> 00:43:50,083
Leave if that's all you have to say.

857
00:44:15,253 --> 00:44:16,983
Hi, Tae Soo.

858
00:44:17,083 --> 00:44:19,353
Why are you coming out from that room?

859
00:44:19,383 --> 00:44:20,983
You should go in.

860
00:44:21,083 --> 00:44:22,353
Eun Ok's sick.

861
00:44:22,883 --> 00:44:23,983
What?

862
00:44:25,983 --> 00:44:26,983
Honey.

863
00:44:28,753 --> 00:44:30,723
What's wrong?

864
00:44:32,353 --> 00:44:34,082
You're burning up.

865
00:44:34,083 --> 00:44:35,403
Get up, let's go to the hospital.

866
00:44:35,483 --> 00:44:37,083
Goodness. There's no need for that.

867
00:44:37,623 --> 00:44:39,783
I took some pills and I feel fine now.

868
00:44:40,383 --> 00:44:41,483
The fever's coming down.

869
00:44:44,583 --> 00:44:46,183
You need to rest at home for a few days.

870
00:44:46,353 --> 00:44:48,553
What are you talking about?
What about our business?

871
00:44:48,623 --> 00:44:50,353
You need a break.

872
00:44:50,383 --> 00:44:52,553
I can work with Sung Koo.

873
00:44:52,623 --> 00:44:53,753
We have your sister, too.

874
00:44:54,183 --> 00:44:55,383
Don't say that.

875
00:44:55,483 --> 00:44:57,383
I can't let my will be broken.

876
00:44:57,583 --> 00:44:59,723
I sure there will be many
more days like this.

877
00:44:59,753 --> 00:45:01,753
How can I take a break every time?

878
00:45:02,453 --> 00:45:04,353
You're so stubborn.

879
00:45:06,983 --> 00:45:09,653
I feel so much better after
seeing my handsome husband.

880
00:45:11,853 --> 00:45:12,853
Honey.

881
00:45:13,183 --> 00:45:15,083
Thank you for working so hard.

882
00:45:15,723 --> 00:45:17,753
I feel like you've finally
got on the right track.

883
00:45:17,883 --> 00:45:19,753
It puts me at ease.

884
00:45:20,383 --> 00:45:21,783
Although I'm physically tired,

885
00:45:21,883 --> 00:45:23,883
I can sleep well.

886
00:45:25,253 --> 00:45:26,983
Then, why are you sick?

887
00:45:29,083 --> 00:45:30,283
Go to bed.

888
00:45:30,853 --> 00:45:34,083
You have to get well for you to work again.

889
00:45:34,353 --> 00:45:35,753
You need to sleep, too.

890
00:45:35,853 --> 00:45:37,453
Let's go out early tomorrow.

891
00:45:37,483 --> 00:45:39,453
I went out early today,

892
00:45:39,483 --> 00:45:40,883
and it seemed like there were...

893
00:45:40,983 --> 00:45:43,383
a lot of people passing our food
truck on their way to work.

894
00:45:43,883 --> 00:45:45,853
Let's try to get more
customers in the morning.

895
00:45:46,453 --> 00:45:48,083
Okay, let's do that.

896
00:45:48,753 --> 00:45:49,853
Go to bed.

897
00:46:30,623 --> 00:46:33,283
(Please allow me to get through the day.)

898
00:46:35,283 --> 00:46:38,683
We know that you are the head
of the gangsters at Choongshim.

899
00:46:38,753 --> 00:46:40,583
There must be a misunderstanding.

900
00:46:40,653 --> 00:46:42,753
My husband has nothing to
do with them any more.

901
00:46:42,853 --> 00:46:45,853
I don't want you to get involved
with Choongshim from now on.

902
00:46:47,283 --> 00:46:49,083
Thinking about what they
made us go through,

903
00:46:49,283 --> 00:46:50,983
makes me shudder.

904
00:46:51,783 --> 00:46:52,823
Okay?

905
00:46:52,883 --> 00:46:55,323
After what happened to our store,
he fell ill from the shock.

906
00:46:55,353 --> 00:46:56,553
You gangsters...

907
00:46:56,683 --> 00:46:58,623
broke my family apart.

908
00:46:58,683 --> 00:46:59,983
Let me make myself clear.

909
00:47:00,383 --> 00:47:02,483
I won't let you do that to me again.

910
00:47:19,483 --> 00:47:22,353
Gosh, it's so cold.

911
00:47:22,383 --> 00:47:23,753
And there are no customers.

912
00:47:23,983 --> 00:47:26,983
That's weird, I thought we
would have more business.

913
00:47:27,853 --> 00:47:29,083
How are you feeling?

914
00:47:30,123 --> 00:47:31,603
You still have the chills, don't you?

915
00:47:32,283 --> 00:47:33,583
It's not that bad.

916
00:47:33,753 --> 00:47:35,823
We still have time until lunch.

917
00:47:35,883 --> 00:47:37,683
Go get some rest.

918
00:47:37,983 --> 00:47:39,583
No, it'd be a waste of time.

919
00:47:41,853 --> 00:47:43,383
Then stay here.

920
00:47:43,753 --> 00:47:45,383
I'll go get you some honey tea.

921
00:47:46,783 --> 00:47:47,783
Thank you.

922
00:48:10,853 --> 00:48:11,983
Get out of the way.

923
00:48:12,083 --> 00:48:14,883
You still don't get it, do you?

924
00:48:16,253 --> 00:48:17,383
What are you doing?

925
00:48:17,883 --> 00:48:21,283
Why are you still in business?

926
00:48:21,553 --> 00:48:23,653
You should leave since you
received compensation.

927
00:48:23,753 --> 00:48:26,483
I told you, we need proper compensation.

928
00:48:26,583 --> 00:48:28,483
Look at this punk...

929
00:48:28,583 --> 00:48:30,253
talk back at me.

930
00:48:30,823 --> 00:48:32,853
Are you trying to play us...

931
00:48:33,383 --> 00:48:34,882
to get more money out of it?

932
00:48:34,883 --> 00:48:36,983
I don't know what your talking about.

933
00:48:37,083 --> 00:48:39,853
- You little... - Don't you dare touch him.

934
00:48:39,883 --> 00:48:41,183
I'll call the police.

935
00:48:41,253 --> 00:48:43,883
Please, call the police for us.

936
00:48:43,983 --> 00:48:46,453
Let's ask them who's here illegally.

937
00:48:46,483 --> 00:48:49,043
We don't have any reason to budge
until our case has been tried.

938
00:48:49,183 --> 00:48:51,453
Our attorney told us that
we can win this case.

939
00:48:51,583 --> 00:48:54,783
I was going to do this peacefully,

940
00:48:54,853 --> 00:48:57,053
but if you're going to be
like this, we can't help you.

941
00:48:57,283 --> 00:48:58,723
Shall we start?

942
00:48:58,853 --> 00:49:00,353
- Boys. - Yes.

943
00:49:04,853 --> 00:49:05,883
Stop it!

944
00:49:07,453 --> 00:49:09,753
Hey! Stop it now!

945
00:49:15,383 --> 00:49:17,023
Beob Kyu, what do you think you're doing?

946
00:49:17,853 --> 00:49:19,083
Seriously.

947
00:49:20,553 --> 00:49:23,353
It's none of your business. Stay out of it.

948
00:49:23,383 --> 00:49:24,653
We're doing business right now.

949
00:49:24,923 --> 00:49:28,083
You have no right to be involved in
any matters related to Choongshim!

950
00:49:28,283 --> 00:49:29,653
If that's the case, do it right.

951
00:49:30,553 --> 00:49:32,283
Stop bothering innocent people.

952
00:49:34,883 --> 00:49:37,483
You can't do this, Tae Soo.

953
00:49:37,553 --> 00:49:39,583
You think you can do whatever you
want because you've left Choongshim?

954
00:49:39,653 --> 00:49:42,183
I don't want to deal with you any more.
Just leave.

955
00:49:42,283 --> 00:49:44,823
- Tae Soo! - Leave! Are you deaf?

956
00:49:51,383 --> 00:49:54,453
Fine. I can come back another day.

957
00:49:55,583 --> 00:49:57,183
- Let's go! - Yes, Sir.

958
00:49:58,083 --> 00:50:00,383
We'll see you later, okay?

959
00:50:01,753 --> 00:50:04,653
If you move out before that,
it'd be better for all of us!

960
00:50:19,283 --> 00:50:20,283
Are you okay?

961
00:50:21,383 --> 00:50:23,823
You have to be careful
in situations like this.

962
00:50:24,883 --> 00:50:27,283
I know that you're angry, but
your safety is more important.

963
00:50:29,183 --> 00:50:32,083
I'm moving my food truck.
I came to say goodbye.

964
00:50:32,483 --> 00:50:34,523
I hope that the misunderstanding
can be cleared up.

965
00:50:37,853 --> 00:50:38,953
Keep your chin up.

966
00:50:40,283 --> 00:50:41,853
I don't know what to tell you.

967
00:50:46,083 --> 00:50:47,383
Did you plot this with them?

968
00:50:47,453 --> 00:50:50,853
Are you playing good cop bad cop?

969
00:50:57,983 --> 00:51:01,853
All I can say is that I'm sorry.

970
00:51:02,353 --> 00:51:04,113
What do you mean there's
nothing you can do?

971
00:51:04,453 --> 00:51:05,883
You can help us.

972
00:51:09,253 --> 00:51:11,883
What's wrong with you? You're
asking a gangster to help us?

973
00:51:13,653 --> 00:51:17,253
You held a high position when
you were at Choongshim, right?

974
00:51:17,883 --> 00:51:19,453
Then you should be able to help us.

975
00:51:33,453 --> 00:51:34,553
No.

976
00:51:35,753 --> 00:51:37,193
My husband doesn't do that any more.

977
00:51:37,723 --> 00:51:39,353
He has nothing to do with Choongshim.

978
00:51:39,583 --> 00:51:40,583
Honey.

979
00:51:41,653 --> 00:51:42,753
Tell them.

980
00:51:43,183 --> 00:51:45,583
You promised me to never get
involved with Choongshim again.

981
00:52:00,683 --> 00:52:01,683
I'm...

982
00:52:02,483 --> 00:52:03,623
I'm sorry.

983
00:52:04,623 --> 00:52:06,453
I'm not in a position to help you.

984
00:52:08,183 --> 00:52:10,453
Everyone, I'm so sorry.

985
00:52:14,083 --> 00:52:15,753
I hate to say this to you,

986
00:52:17,253 --> 00:52:18,893
but you won't be able to win this battle.

987
00:52:20,083 --> 00:52:21,283
End it here.

988
00:52:22,353 --> 00:52:23,983
I don't want you to get hurt.

989
00:52:24,483 --> 00:52:25,583
No.

990
00:52:27,853 --> 00:52:30,653
Whether you help me or not,
I will fight Choongshim.

991
00:52:32,753 --> 00:52:33,853
I can't back off now.

992
00:52:37,283 --> 00:52:39,753
Let's go. We should to back
to our food truck now.

993
00:52:40,653 --> 00:52:41,653
Hurry up.

994
00:52:54,183 --> 00:52:56,653
What? Tae Soo got involved?

995
00:52:56,753 --> 00:52:59,283
Why would Tae Soo get involved in this?

996
00:52:59,883 --> 00:53:02,083
Well... I don't really know.

997
00:53:02,883 --> 00:53:05,023
Anyway, because of Tae Soo,

998
00:53:05,383 --> 00:53:07,553
those jerks at Manbok
Shophouse think they can win.

999
00:53:10,083 --> 00:53:13,353
He makes my life difficult
even after leaving Choongshim.

1000
00:53:14,653 --> 00:53:18,353
Well, shouldn't we do something about it?

1001
00:53:20,883 --> 00:53:21,883
You're right.

1002
00:53:24,653 --> 00:53:26,353
Write your name and sign at the bottom.

1003
00:53:27,853 --> 00:53:28,853
What is this?

1004
00:53:28,953 --> 00:53:30,753
(I, Yoon Tae Soo, will never
get involved with Choongshim.)

1005
00:53:30,853 --> 00:53:31,853
Goodness.

1006
00:53:32,553 --> 00:53:35,983
Is this a joke? Are you seriously
asking me to sign this?

1007
00:53:36,353 --> 00:53:39,183
I'm doing this because I can't trust you.

1008
00:53:39,553 --> 00:53:42,683
Sign it. And report to me even
when you go to the bathroom.

1009
00:53:42,883 --> 00:53:45,653
I couldn't just walk by, so I
said a few things. That's all.

1010
00:53:46,083 --> 00:53:49,083
It was a good chance to clear up the
misunderstanding with them, too.

1011
00:53:49,183 --> 00:53:51,663
Then you could've just talked to them.
You made me wait and...

1012
00:53:52,783 --> 00:53:54,703
Why were you listening to
them ask you for help?

1013
00:53:55,553 --> 00:53:58,083
My heart sank when I saw you hesitate.

1014
00:53:59,283 --> 00:54:00,353
This way.

1015
00:54:02,753 --> 00:54:04,183
Hey! Tae Soo!

1016
00:54:06,983 --> 00:54:08,083
Hello, Eun Ok.

1017
00:54:08,853 --> 00:54:10,383
What's this?

1018
00:54:10,983 --> 00:54:13,823
"I, Yoon Tae Soo, will never
get involved with Choongshim."

1019
00:54:14,453 --> 00:54:16,553
Yes. This is great.

1020
00:54:17,123 --> 00:54:19,183
Eun Ok, I've always known
that you're the wise one.

1021
00:54:20,483 --> 00:54:21,623
Why are you here?

1022
00:54:21,723 --> 00:54:24,083
I came her for the kimchi fried rice.
Why else?

1023
00:54:24,383 --> 00:54:25,653
Can I get two servings?

1024
00:54:29,553 --> 00:54:31,253
Are you done for the day?

1025
00:54:32,083 --> 00:54:35,383
Why would we close up already?
I'll make it for you now.

1026
00:54:36,253 --> 00:54:38,723
Thank you. That looks good.

1027
00:54:39,353 --> 00:54:40,553
Spare me a second.

1028
00:54:48,383 --> 00:54:49,453
What do you want to talk to me about?

1029
00:54:49,553 --> 00:54:51,383
Stay out of things that are
none of your business.

1030
00:54:51,453 --> 00:54:53,453
Just focus on your own business.

1031
00:54:53,553 --> 00:54:55,083
Do your job properly.

1032
00:54:55,883 --> 00:54:59,183
Why can't you give them what
they rightfully deserve?

1033
00:54:59,753 --> 00:55:01,353
Doing so won't hurt Choongshim at all.

1034
00:55:01,753 --> 00:55:03,883
Rather, it'll improve the company's image.

1035
00:55:05,453 --> 00:55:09,383
Tae Soo. Everyone is telling
me what to do these days.

1036
00:55:09,453 --> 00:55:12,883
Dad lectures at me. Even Do Kyung
and Hyun Ji tell me what to do.

1037
00:55:12,983 --> 00:55:15,453
And now, you're going to
join them and lecture me?

1038
00:55:16,253 --> 00:55:18,983
Mind your own business and make fried rice.

1039
00:55:19,353 --> 00:55:22,083
People's lives were ruined because of us.

1040
00:55:22,183 --> 00:55:23,853
Have some decency and don't
take them down again.

1041
00:55:23,883 --> 00:55:26,603
Stop worrying about other people.
Worry about keeping your own life!

1042
00:55:26,653 --> 00:55:28,983
- Are you threatening me now?
- I'm not threatening you.

1043
00:55:30,453 --> 00:55:31,733
I'm giving you a word of advice.

1044
00:55:32,083 --> 00:55:34,123
Anyway, this is the last
advice I'll be giving you.

1045
00:55:34,623 --> 00:55:35,823
You know what's next, right?

1046
00:55:37,083 --> 00:55:38,563
What if I tell you that I don't know?

1047
00:55:41,653 --> 00:55:43,653
Here's your kimchi fried rice.

1048
00:55:44,553 --> 00:55:46,283
Thanks, Eun Ok.

1049
00:55:47,553 --> 00:55:48,753
You should go.

1050
00:55:49,753 --> 00:55:52,083
I'm sure Tae Soo understood
everything you said.

1051
00:55:54,183 --> 00:55:55,883
Yes, I shall.

1052
00:55:56,723 --> 00:55:58,753
Tae Soo. I'm going now.

1053
00:55:59,883 --> 00:56:01,083
Beob Kyu, let's go!

1054
00:56:03,853 --> 00:56:05,553
Goodness.

1055
00:56:11,553 --> 00:56:15,083
Fine. I'll sign it.

1056
00:56:17,083 --> 00:56:19,353
Mr Choi. What are you talking about now?

1057
00:56:19,923 --> 00:56:23,083
What have I done to them?
Why are they suing me now?

1058
00:56:23,283 --> 00:56:24,683
Gosh. This is making my blood boil.

1059
00:56:26,883 --> 00:56:27,983
I'll get back to you.

1060
00:56:30,653 --> 00:56:32,882
Are they suing you?

1061
00:56:32,883 --> 00:56:35,383
They're targeting me now because
they haven't been able...

1062
00:56:35,453 --> 00:56:38,083
to get anything out of Choongshim.

1063
00:56:38,183 --> 00:56:40,883
These jerks. They have no idea
what they're dealing with.

1064
00:56:40,983 --> 00:56:43,253
Ki Beom. Let's teach them a lesson.

1065
00:56:43,553 --> 00:56:45,753
We've been too easy on them.

1066
00:57:00,083 --> 00:57:01,083
Hello?

1067
00:57:02,453 --> 00:57:04,753
It's me, Chul, from Manbok Shophouse.

1068
00:57:06,853 --> 00:57:08,183
Who? Chul?

1069
00:57:09,983 --> 00:57:11,653
The gangsters from Choongshim...

1070
00:57:12,553 --> 00:57:15,653
are vandalising our store right now!
Can you help us?

1071
00:57:17,253 --> 00:57:18,253
Please help us!

1072
00:57:22,723 --> 00:57:25,253
- Chul, it's... - Please help us!

1073
00:57:25,853 --> 00:57:27,823
You're the only one who can help us.

1074
00:57:28,653 --> 00:57:31,353
- Stop it! - Move out of the way.

1075
00:57:33,883 --> 00:57:34,883
Chul. Chul!

1076
00:57:39,083 --> 00:57:41,353
What's going on? Manbok Shophouse?

1077
00:57:41,883 --> 00:57:43,553
- They called you? - Yes.

1078
00:57:44,553 --> 00:57:46,353
I think Choongshim sent some guys.

1079
00:57:47,353 --> 00:57:50,153
That boy is Sung Min's age. He was
probably staying up all night to...

1080
00:57:50,753 --> 00:57:52,183
protect his shop.

1081
00:57:52,883 --> 00:57:55,883
So? Are you going to run over there?

1082
00:57:59,283 --> 00:58:00,283
Gosh.

1083
00:58:01,653 --> 00:58:02,753
Are you?

1084
00:58:03,653 --> 00:58:04,753
Goodness.

1085
00:58:08,853 --> 00:58:09,853
Well...

1086
00:58:11,183 --> 00:58:13,283
I promised you I wouldn't.

1087
00:58:14,283 --> 00:58:15,353
I'm not going.

1088
00:58:19,083 --> 00:58:20,083
Go back to sleep now.

1089
00:58:23,383 --> 00:58:26,823
- Honey. - I'm not going.

1090
00:58:32,553 --> 00:58:34,553
I'm getting myself a glass of water.

1091
00:58:35,983 --> 00:58:36,983
Go back to sleep.

1092
00:59:45,983 --> 00:59:47,453
Get off of him.

1093
00:59:48,083 --> 00:59:50,653
You're the boss here, right?

1094
00:59:50,723 --> 00:59:52,283
Please make them stop!

1095
00:59:52,383 --> 00:59:53,783
You don't remember me, do you?

1096
00:59:54,183 --> 00:59:56,283
I won't let you do that to me again.

1097
00:59:56,383 --> 00:59:57,783
You can help us.

1098
00:59:57,883 --> 01:00:00,283
You held a high position when
you were at Choongshim, right?

1099
01:00:00,483 --> 01:00:01,883
Then you should be able to help us.

1100
01:00:04,253 --> 01:00:05,783
Can you help us?

1101
01:00:07,083 --> 01:00:08,353
Please help us.

1102
01:00:08,483 --> 01:00:10,383
You're the only one who can help us.

1103
01:00:17,683 --> 01:00:20,483
I don't want you to get involved
with Choongshim from now on.

1104
01:00:21,353 --> 01:00:23,113
Thinking about what they
made us go through,

1105
01:00:23,253 --> 01:00:24,983
makes me shudder.

1106
01:00:25,683 --> 01:00:26,723
Honey.

1107
01:00:27,253 --> 01:00:28,953
Thank you for working so hard.

1108
01:00:30,083 --> 01:00:32,083
I feel like you've finally
got on the right track.

1109
01:00:32,353 --> 01:00:33,823
It puts me at ease.

1110
01:00:34,783 --> 01:00:36,123
Although I'm physically tired,

1111
01:00:36,383 --> 01:00:38,183
I can sleep well.

1112
01:00:38,783 --> 01:00:39,823
No.

1113
01:00:41,183 --> 01:00:42,823
My husband doesn't do that any more.

1114
01:00:42,883 --> 01:00:44,683
He has nothing to do with Choongshim.

1115
01:00:44,783 --> 01:00:46,483
Write your name and sign at the bottom.

1116
01:00:46,583 --> 01:00:48,503
Why were you listening to
them ask you for help?

1117
01:00:49,353 --> 01:00:51,983
My heart sank when I saw you hesitate.

1118
01:01:08,083 --> 01:01:09,083
Go.

1119
01:01:24,823 --> 01:01:26,783
I must have been destined to be...

1120
01:01:27,083 --> 01:01:28,783
a wife of a gangster.

1121
01:01:31,453 --> 01:01:33,483
I thought 18 years was enough.

1122
01:01:34,823 --> 01:01:36,623
I wanted to live like a normal person.

1123
01:01:38,883 --> 01:01:40,683
But I guess it's not in the stars for me.

1124
01:01:45,183 --> 01:01:46,783
I won't be able to stop if I go now.

1125
01:01:48,253 --> 01:01:49,733
I'll have to help them until the end.

1126
01:01:52,253 --> 01:01:53,983
You think I don't know that?

1127
01:01:58,553 --> 01:01:59,583
Go.

1128
01:02:01,083 --> 01:02:02,583
Go save the country or go save a man.

1129
01:02:03,553 --> 01:02:04,883
Do whatever you want.

1130
01:02:06,823 --> 01:02:08,653
- Honey. - Go!

1131
01:02:09,723 --> 01:02:11,483
Go before I change my mind.

1132
01:02:50,583 --> 01:02:52,583
(Sweet and Scary Family)

1133
01:02:53,183 --> 01:02:54,453
You'll be going behind bars.

1134
01:02:54,483 --> 01:02:56,163
Drop the lawsuit against Manbok Shophouse.

1135
01:02:56,483 --> 01:02:58,383
Did you stick your nose in
someone else's business?

1136
01:02:58,483 --> 01:02:59,982
Will it get you in trouble?

1137
01:02:59,983 --> 01:03:01,283
You're not living this life alone.

1138
01:03:01,353 --> 01:03:03,083
You need to look around and help others.

1139
01:03:03,183 --> 01:03:05,983
Mr Park called and said
that he's going to quit.

1140
01:03:06,083 --> 01:03:07,483
How can you fight without a lawyer?

1141
01:03:07,553 --> 01:03:09,353
If you want to win, you need to toughen up.

1142
01:03:09,383 --> 01:03:10,753
We will lose if we don't unite.

1143
01:03:10,883 --> 01:03:12,583
You need to question me
at the police station?

1144
01:03:12,653 --> 01:03:14,083
You don't have to be someone I'm proud of.

1145
01:03:14,183 --> 01:03:15,583
But don't be the person I am ashamed of.

1146
01:03:15,653 --> 01:03:18,353
Mum, let's move back to our old house.

1147
01:03:18,483 --> 01:03:19,653
For the last three years,

1148
01:03:19,723 --> 01:03:21,453
I was really happy...

1149
01:03:21,483 --> 01:03:22,883
and thankful.

1150
01:03:22,983 --> 01:03:24,883
Just let me go.

1151
01:03:25,723 --> 01:03:27,883
Why are you waiting for someone
that's not going to come?

1152
01:03:27,983 --> 01:03:30,483
We have to leave this
place if we want to live.

1153
01:03:30,783 --> 01:03:32,983
Attacking them first can
be our best defence.

1154
01:03:33,083 --> 01:03:34,083
I apologise.

1155
01:03:34,183 --> 01:03:36,623
I calculated the compensation,

1156
01:03:36,783 --> 01:03:39,023
and it turns out you should
be getting twice the amount.

1157
01:03:39,083 --> 01:03:41,783
We want you out of this.

1158
01:03:41,883 --> 01:03:44,623
With money and power, you can do anything.

1159
01:03:44,683 --> 01:03:45,983
Boss!

1160
01:04:16,183 --> 01:04:17,883
The Family Court is always full.

1161
01:04:17,983 --> 01:04:19,083
(Go Dong Mi, never had a boyfriend)

1162
01:04:19,183 --> 01:04:22,753
You should be suspicious.
Reasonable suspicion is important.

1163
01:04:22,783 --> 01:04:24,223
(Baek Da Jeong, soon to be divorced)

1164
01:04:24,283 --> 01:04:26,983
Bring me the big ones. As big as melons!

1165
01:04:27,083 --> 01:04:28,083
(Hong Ae Ran, soon to be married)

1166
01:04:28,283 --> 01:04:30,383
(A romantic comedy with a cheerful energy)

1167
01:04:30,623 --> 01:04:33,383
(Happy Ending Once Again)

